b'\xe2\x80\xa6I think the rest of the world has no idea of the involvement. It takes so much dedication and care from everyone who works on it.'
b'\xe2\x80\xa6Carnival is very important to Brazil and is known around the world for being the ultimate joy filled celebration...'
